    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes the motivation for, and benefits of, applying Segment Routing (SR) in BGP-based large-scale data centers.  It describes the design to deploy SR in those data centers for both the MPLS and IPv6 data planes.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
